<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634136031139988001" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634136032724862180">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The example contains <em>RadioButton </em>and 'TextAlign' and 'CheckAlign' ComboBoxes. The 'TextAlign' ComboBox contains all enable text alignment and the 'CheckAlign' ComboBox contains all enable radio box alignment. Select item in the 'TextAlign' ComboBox and <em>RadioButton </em>text alignment will be changed respectively. Select item in the 'CheckAlign' ComboBox and <em>RadioButton </em>check alignment will be changed.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>RadioButton </em>control contains <em>CheckAlign </em>and <em>TextAlign </em>properties. The <em>CheckAlign</em> defines the radio box alignment on the <em>RadioButton </em>control. The <em>TextAlign </em>defines the text alignment on the <em>RadioButton </em>control. These properties can be contains the following values:<br /><strong>TopLeft </strong>&ndash; radio box/text/check box is vertically aligned at the top, and horizontally aligned on the left;<br /><strong>TopCenter </strong>- radio box/text is vertically aligned at the top, and horizontally aligned at the center;<br /><strong>TopRight </strong>- radio box/text is vertically aligned at the top, and horizontally aligned on the right;<br /><strong>MiddleLeft </strong>- radio box/text is vertically aligned in the middle, and horizontally aligned on the left;<br /><strong>MiddleCenter </strong>- radio box/text is vertically aligned in the middle, and horizontally aligned at the center;<br /><strong>MiddleRight </strong>- radio box/text is vertically aligned in the middle, and horizontally aligned on the right;<br /><strong>BottomLeft </strong>- radio box/text is vertically aligned at the bottom, and horizontally aligned on the left;<br /><strong>BottomCenter </strong>- radio box/text is vertically aligned at the bottom, and horizontally aligned at the center;<br /><strong>BottomRight </strong>- radio box/text is vertically aligned at the bottom, and horizontally aligned on the right.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
